t a flame....Not a bad idea really. *Cough cough* Ugh! I can\'t even stay here long enough to destroy them. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"map-item barracks-map-item\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group map-item barracks-map-item\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"map-item-modal graeme\"} -->\n<p class=\"map-item-modal graeme\">My home away from home. These barracks have served me well in my stay in Orbem. After John and I disabled the security system this building has gone through some major interior design changes. Ioana wouldn\'t stop complaining about it not being \"comfortable\" enough. I mean we live in Caninth Village most days so I didn\'t see the point. I do have to admit she really upgraded the hangout ability in the lab. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->','Explore','','inherit','closed','closed','','173-revision-v1','','','2020-11-10 23:39:42','2020-11-10 23:39:42','',173,'https://orbemorder.local/173-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
