t a flame....Not a bad idea really. *Cough cough* Ugh! I can\'t even stay here long enough to destroy them. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"map-item barracks-map-item\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group map-item barracks-map-item\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"map-item-modal graeme\"} -->\n<p class=\"map-item-modal graeme\">My home away from home. These barracks have served me well in my stay in Orbem. We were getting attacked by security robots every few days until recently. I\'m pretty sure I got rid of the last one. Ioana wasn\'t too happy about being stuck in a red orb. I guess she didn\'t find it as relaxing as John did.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"map-item-modal sionnah\"} -->\n<p class=\"map-item-modal sionnah\">I cannot believe I am actually here! The Homonian base. So much history took place here. I need to get Graeme to grant me entry into this relic of the past. If it was not for the thousands of deceased victims lying around this would be a beautiful place. I will check a window.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"map-item-modal corinder\"} -->\n<p class=\"map-item-modal corinder\">Ah my old stomp\'n grounds. I\'ve spent a minute rummaging through these old bones for scrap. I remember meet\'n Mr. Graeme here. This building sure is spooky though. I could hear strange noises coming from these wall. Graeme said it was probably just security bots. Whatever that is.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"map-item-modal koromere\"} -->\n<p class=\"map-item-modal koromere\">Yes. The Homonian stronghold. I remember those cowards holding themselves in here. Hiding like the rats they are. If I wasn\'t commanding a grand army I would\'ve destroyed this building with them in it. Oh shoot is that Graeme in the window? Gotta go!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"map-item aster-farm-map-item\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group map-item aster-farm-map-item\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"map-item-modal graeme\"} -->\n<p class=\"map-item-modal graeme\">Hey, there\'s uncle Aster\'s farm. I wonder in Jeek is around. Man I loved riding those porvets. I\'ve never rode something so fast and smooth. I bet Alstra is sleeping. Yep there she is. Lazy lady as always. Almost got me killed that one.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"map-item-modal corinder\"} -->\n<p class=\"map-item-modal corinder\">So this is where my mate Bulrok came from. Oh I see the big bugger over there! Hey friend, how have you been? Wow, so many porvets. Look at the little scamps with their mum. I sure love the forest, but maybe I could get used to farm life? </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"map-item-modal sionnah\"} -->\n<p class=\"map-item-modal sionnah\">It is great to be back at my uncle\'s farm. I used to spend days here riding every porvet on the ranch. I wonder if the old Hari-man is around. Oh hello there Jeek. You are looking quite lovely. I would love to take your for a ride, but I believe I will continue walking for now.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"map-item-modal koromere\"} -->\n<p class=\"map-item-modal koromere\">Oh. A ranch. Full of domesticated beasts. How quaint. The smell is horrible. I do fancy a nocturnal version of one of these \"porvets\", I believe they\'re called. Much sharper claws though. Perhaps a few more eyes as well. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"map-item caninth-village-map-item\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group map-item caninth-village-map-item\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"map-item-modal corinder\"} -->\n<p class=\"map-item-modal corinder\">Ah, the happiest place in Orbem. Caninth Village. I can just smell the tasty meats waiting for me to eat. I should really go say hi to me mum. I know she\'s been worried after the adventure I\'ve had. Could use a nap as well. And some meat.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"map-item-modal graeme\"} -->\n<p class=\"map-item-modal graeme\">Great to be home. The first place I felt accepted in Orbem. The Caninth sure are a lovely species. I sure could use a giant Jeroke hug right now. He\'s probably too busy. Well I should check in with the others. I\'m sure they\'re at Corinder\'s or that new bar Genie started. Some dwice doesn\'t sound half bad.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"map-item ioana-map-item\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group map-item ioana-map-item\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"map-item-modal graeme\"} -->\n<p class=\"map-item-modal graeme\">My love! I missed you. What are you doing out here? You can\'t be standing around alone. Oh, Genie is meeting you here? Alright I guess you two ladies have proven yourselves enough to hold your own in Orbem. I\'m going to walk around more. Love you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"map-item forno-map-item\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group map-item forno-map-item\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"map-item-modal corinder\"} -->\n<p class=\"map-item-modal corinder\">Back off Forno! You and your Redfang chumps don\'t run Blackclaw Forest! Just because I\'m not around to keep you thugs in check as much, doesn\'t mean Jeroke aint the Grand clan leader. Now off with you or I\'ll call my friend Graeme to teach you another lesson.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"map-item wonderland-map-item\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group map-item wonderland-map-item\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":193,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://orbemorder.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/spacer.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-193\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"map-item-modal graeme\"} -->\n<p class=\"map-item-modal graeme\">Welcome to Wonderland. I still can\'t believe Schmelwick thought name was a good idea. I wonder if Gralland is around. Even though he\'s Elven royalty, I kind of took a liking to him. Uh oh there\'s some guards coming. Better hide. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"map-item deathwood-manor-map-item\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group map-item deathwood-manor-map-item\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":193,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://orbemorder.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/spacer.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-193\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"map-item-modal koromere\"} -->\n<p class=\"map-item-modal koromere\">My lovely castle, Deathwood Manor. Usually I would\'ve felt immense pleasure returning back to my home. After my fight with Graeme, I lost more than my home. Not having my faithful pet, Syrinae, to greet me is uncomfortable. All the more reason to continue my plans of revenge!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"map-item scarlett-map-item\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group map-item scarlett-map-item\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"map-item-modal graeme\"} -->\n<p class=\"map-item-modal graeme\">Hey Scarlett, how are you? You\'re my special little girl. I gotta go walk around Orbem some more, but I\'ll see you really soon. Go say hi to mommy for me. I love you!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->','Explore','','inherit','closed','closed','','173-revision-v1','','','2020-11-14 22:00:21','2020-11-14 22:00:21','',173,'https://orbemorder.local/173-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (226,1,'2020-11-15 05:36:12','2020-11-15 05:36:12','<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"map-item orbem-academy-map-item\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group map-item orbem-academy-map-item\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":193,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://orbemorder.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/spacer.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-193\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"map-item-modal graeme\"} -->\n<p class=\"map-item-modal graeme\">Wow! Orbem Academy is bigger than I remember. I wonder if Sionnah is giving a lecture. I\'d like to have her show me around. Better not bug her too much. I know she probably has a lot to catch up on work wise. Maybe I pop in the library and see if there\'s anything interest to read. I doubt I have enough time in the day to get through all the genres.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->','Gillimank','','publish','closed','closed','','gillimank','','','2020-11-15 08:23:00','2020-11-15 08:23:00','',0,'https://orbemorder.local/?post_type=explore-area&#038;p=226',0,'explore-area','',0);
